HEADWORD: Macauco
<hw>Ma*cau"co</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of small lemurs, as <spn>Lemur
murinus</spn>, which resembles a rat in size.</def>⟦br⟧
